title: Unreal Operation Na Pali Playthrough -- Part 3
description: Finished on Hard! Honestly this mod was impressive. The level design and actual gameplay of it was solid. The voice acting was bad yet really funny so I enjoyed it. It was cool playing a single player game with the unreal tournament weapons.
